#: ../../../../docstring of numpy.invert:27
msgid ""
"This condition is broadcast over the input. At locations where the condition "
"is True, the `out` array will be set to the ufunc result. Elsewhere, the "
"`out` array will retain its original value. Note that if an uninitialized "
"`out` array is created via the default ``out=None``, locations within it "
"where the condition is False will remain uninitialized."
msgstr ""

